3112   1          // note 4_b. 12bit : (M / N / Divs) = (2 / 3 * Ratio) --> M = N * Divs * (2 / 3 * Ratio), N or Divs: m
             -ultiple of 3
3113   1          // note 4_b. 16bit : (M / N / Divs) = (1 / 2 * Ratio) --> M = N * Divs * (1 / 2 * Ratio), N or Divs: m
